comments.content:
The original should be **[Princetown](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317133658/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/letraset/princetown/)** by Dick Jones (1981, Letraset) and it's an outline font  
There are also some solid versions from font-forgery companies as SoftMaker, Art&Letters, etc
